---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Talia Sable" description="Nerd, hippie, writer, ex-programmer, businesswoman">
	<div class="hero">
		<picture>
			<source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/body-bluebathroom.jpg" />
			<img src="/header-lilies.jpg" alt="Talia Sable" class="hero-image" loading="eager" />
		</picture>
	</div>

	<article class="about">
		<section class="intro-section">
			<h1>An Introduction</h1>
			<p class="tagline">When we talk about who we are, what we choose to say is revealing. It's never the whole picture. Here I do my best to feed you enough morsels of myself for you to decide:</p>
			<p class="question">Walk away or come closer?</p>
		</section>

		<section class="bio">
			<p>I'm a nerd, a hippie, a writer, an ex-programmer, a businesswoman. I chase growth and unusual experiences. I have social anxiety and a burning desire to connect.</p>
			<p>This is my vague outline, the shadow on the wall. I look forward to revealing myself more fully.</p>
		</section>

		<div class="content-with-photo">
			<div class="stats-container">
				<section class="stats">
					<h2>Stats</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>Ethnicity: Eurasian</li>
						<li>Height: 5'1"</li>
						<li>Bust: 32C</li>
						<li>Waist: 27"</li>
						<li>Weight: 105lbs</li>
						<li>Hips: 37"</li>
						<li>Shoe size: 37IT</li>
					</ul>
					<ul>
						<li>Countries visited: 24</li>
						<li>Myers-Briggs: INTJ</li>
						<li>Enneagram: 4w3</li>
					</ul>
				</section>
			</div>
			<div class="photo-insert">
				<img src="/body-bluedress2.jpg" alt="Talia Sable" />
			</div>
		</div>

		<section class="facets">
			<h2>The Sides of the Dice</h2>
			<p class="section-intro">Facets of myself I bring to the table</p>

			<div class="facets-grid">
				<div class="facet">
					<h3>Empath: Compassion in presence</h3>
					<p>I dive into the emotional deep end. Things can get weird down there, but it's cozy to cuddle and share intimately. I'm not afraid of intense or difficult emotions.</p>
					<p class="examples">Massages and oxytocin. Silent eye contact. Authentic relating.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="facet">
					<h3>Diogenes: Playfulness in intellect</h3>
					<p>To put it gently, I'm a huge nerd. Let's investigate ideas with curiosity and goodnatured irreverence.</p>
					<p class="examples">AI. Supply chains. DnD. How brains work. Ethics. Consciousness. Narratives and frames.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="facet">
					<h3>Sensate: Bliss of the moment</h3>
					<p>I'm "energetically sensitive," whatever that means. Small sensations (the electricity of a small touch) reach deep into my core.</p>
					<p class="examples">Slow dances. Beauty in the mundane. Divine comedy. Plein air watercoloring.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="facet">
					<h3>Adventurer: Delight in the novel</h3>
					<p>Ooh, novelty. The fear? That makes the growth more delicious. There's something very intimate about trying something for the first time with someone.</p>
					<p class="examples">Challenges and becoming stronger. Climbing, BJJ, hitchhiking.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer class="about-footer">
			<p>More of my writing on <a href="https://taliasable.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Substack</a></p>
		</footer>
	</article>

	<section class="photo-gallery">
		<div class="gallery-grid">
			<img src="/body-facecloseup.jpg" alt="Talia Sable" />
			<img src="/body-fountain.jpg" alt="Talia Sable" />
			<img src="/body-reachingback.jpg" alt="Talia Sable" />
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="footer-image">
		<img src="/header-reading.jpg" alt="Talia Sable" />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.hero {
		width: 100%;
		height: 70vh;
		min-height: 500px;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.hero-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center;
		display: block;
	}

	.about {
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 1.5rem 2rem 4rem;
	}

	.intro-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.intro-section h1 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}

	.question {
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-size: 1.3rem;
	}

	.bio {
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.bio p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.content-with-photo {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.photo-insert img {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		display: block;
	}

	.stats {
		background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
	}

	.stats h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.stats ul {
		list-style: none;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.stats ul:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.stats li {
		padding: 0.4rem 0;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.facets {
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.facets h2 {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.section-intro {
		font-style: italic;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.facets-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.facet {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
		border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
	}

	.facet h3 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.facet p {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.examples {
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	.about-footer {
		text-align: center;
		padding-top: 3rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
		margin-top: 4rem;
	}

	.about-footer a {
		color: var(--color-accent) !important;
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.about-footer a:hover {
		color: var(--color-accent-hover) !important;
	}

	.footer-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: 60vh;
		min-height: 400px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.footer-image img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center;
		display: block;
	}

	.photo-gallery {
		width: 100%;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.gallery-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 0;
	}

	.gallery-grid img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 500px;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center;
		display: block;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.gallery-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.gallery-grid img {
			height: 400px;
		}
		.hero {
			height: 50vh;
			min-height: 400px;
		}

		.about {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.content-with-photo {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.facets-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
	}
</style>
